{"tid":2228383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那買家+支那中間人+墨西哥盜獵者捕獵石首魚魚鰾，仲搞到小頭鼠海豚就黎絕種","createTime":"2020-10-03T13:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T11:46:42.000Z","uid":3873,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"26c158341f8b3fd2e3f00dd143bc5f3b4b02d80d","tid":2228383,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:39:25.000Z","msg":"其實我都唔知算唔算時事。事緣有套叫「魅影海洋」嘅紀錄片，講班保育人士試圖去救小頭鼠海豚，但牽涉到當地墨西哥黑幫嘅非法石首魚交易，之後再講話石首魚魚鰾其實係賣去支那，而喺墨西哥嘅中間人亦都係支那人嚟，佢地會買通當地海關再由墨西哥經香港運去支那<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z0Q0YpxmtyM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZ0Q0YpxmtyM&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdhPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=659be555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z0Q0YpxmtyM</a><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/ch/news/3403663\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taiwannews.com.tw%2Fch%2Fnews%2F3403663&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdhPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=88328686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/ch/news/3403663</a><br />\n《法新社》（AFP）報導，加利福尼亞灣石首魚是墨西哥加利福尼亞灣北區的特有種，已被國際自然保護聯盟列入瀕危物種紅色名錄。非營利組織海洋守護者協會(Sea Shepherd)的巡邏隊一連三年，日夜不停的巡邏就是要避免漁船偷渡石首魚與小頭鼠海豚。但是這些非法盜獵者都擁搶自重，使得加利福尼亞海灣近年成了保育人士、墨西哥海軍船隻與直升機與非法漁民的戰場。<br />\n<br />\n東方日報 - 漁民非法撈捕石首魚 威脅瀕危小頭鼠海豚 / 2019年12月11日<br />\n2019年8月，環保組織海洋牧人協會在墨西哥加尼福尼亞灣，發現6隻瀕臨絕種的小頭鼠海豚，形容消息令人振奮。惟該組織周一（9日）表示，近百名漁民近日在上述水域非法網捕加尼福尼亞灣石首魚，令近10隻年幼的小頭鼠海豚被捕獲。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.pts.org.tw/article/491650\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.pts.org.tw%2Farticle%2F491650&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdhPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=a11784c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.pts.org.tw/article/491650</a><br />\n警方破獲了瀕危物種的「加利福尼亞灣石首魚」乾魚鰾走私案，這是美國FBI通報刑事局，中國有人私下收購魚鰾，以台灣做為中繼站轉運到中國。我國警方和海關，成功攔截到19公斤的乾魚鰾，市價超過新台幣2700萬。<br />\n<br />\n支那人真係好仆街，墨西哥班友仲要買通警察，成個鎮都係佢嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗起仲有單支那漁船入侵南美洲濫捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200925/HC5ZMO3GUFB45BFKJPRKJUSMXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200925%2FHC5ZMO3GUFB45BFKJPRKJUSMXU%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdhPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=4ace3b36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200925%2FHC5ZMO3GUFB45BFKJPRKJUSMXU%2F&h=4779a47c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200925/HC5ZMO3GUFB45BFKJPRKJUSMXU/</a>"},{"pid":"61f7aa83e71e864d427683745dbaba19e0d30aae","tid":2228383,"uid":327169,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:42:13.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">召喚所有怨靈，滅殺支那!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207dac1bb51d1bc05ea1755bc6e19b11c4910fe1","tid":2228383,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:44:15.000Z","msg":"花膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dff08c45c066688e3d363a2d63e717a3154794d","tid":2228383,"uid":53062,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:46:18.000Z","msg":"中醫撚食光全地球物種 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93dead1f23454ef5897d55fd0db30b3071b1c93a","tid":2228383,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:52:33.000Z","msg":"非營利組織海洋守護者協會有冇收錢先"},{"pid":"8879c653c8716cf81a1b7019266e21a86edb2081","tid":2228383,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611005587b2f529e44e76bf9557f0b62c07d2370","tid":2228383,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:55:05.000Z","msg":"唔好再嘈了<br />\n直接核平"},{"pid":"3f0c6c56b97f9bc3985d76bc1faae8b0091ac77d","tid":2228383,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T13:55:19.000Z","msg":"出兵啦"},{"pid":"e1fb9bf2b4a45f157b6394f20233f9d865243e97","tid":2228383,"uid":117893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:23:27.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh<br />\n遠到墨西哥都比支那搞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60807cd932c3b6a3f3568fadc809666983391535","tid":2228383,"uid":117893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"又有香港份做白手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後更新日期：2020-06-08 18:57<br />\n<br />\n海關破獲1宗以冰磚魚柳藏2,500萬元石首魚魚鰾的走私案，為歷來最大宗同類案件。海關上周四（4日）檢查20箱由美國洛杉磯、報稱是鮮魚的空運貨物，因美國運魚來港並不常見，引起人員關注。海關檢查後，發現貨物箱上寫上產地來源為墨西哥，X光機影像揭發貨箱密度不均，竟是以冰磚魚柳蓋在底和面，但中層是名貴的石首魚魚鰾，可製成貴價花膠。20箱貨物中共有15箱藏魚鰾，合共重約160公斤，總值約2,500萬元。海關其後拘捕5名男子，包括倉庫負責人及收貨人。<br />\n<br />\n該批石首魚魚鰾為墨西哥加利福尼亞灣特有品種，因生境破壞及長年過度捕撈，已被列入《瀕危野生動植物種國際貿易公約》附錄I及入國際自然保護聯盟瀕危物種紅名錄中的極危級別。"},{"pid":"543adaba78c820db3bf81541893413b123415f22","tid":2228383,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"啲環保撚 以前唔係咁譴責 日本捕獵鯨魚嘅<im